def min_cost_sort(A):

    """Sort list A in ascending order.

 

    And return the switching cost in sorting.

    """

    B = list(A)

    B.sort()

    cost = 0

    min_w = B[0]

        bi = A.index(b)

            si = A.index(st)

            tmp_cost += b + st

            cost += tmp_cost
